C(k,1) = k 
C(k,k) =1 
C(21,2)= C(20,1) + C(20,2) \\ = C(20,1) + C(19,1) + C(19,2) \\ = C(20,1) + C(19,1) + C(18,1) + C(18,2)  
 C(21,2)=C(20,1) + C(19,1) + C(18,1) + \ldots + C(2,1)+ C(2,2)
 C(21,2)=20+19+18+ \ldots + 2+1 = \frac{20\times 21}2 = 210
{21\choose2} = {20\choose1}+{19\choose1}+{18\choose1}+\cdots+{2\choose1}+{2\choose2}
20+19+18+\cdots+2+1 = \frac{20*21}{2} = 210
 {21\choose2} = \frac{21!}{19!.2!} = 210
